This drawing is one of my recent ones. As you can see the lines are pretty smooth, the shading is soft, and it’s a pretty clean looking piece. The background is quite simple. This drawing took me about an hour! Digital art may take longer than traditional art, but the end result is worth it.<br>I hope you enjoy this page!</p> 
